      "content": "hey i live in oslo and since its winter and basically no sun i've been feeling really low on energy. i read online that taking a super high dose of vitamin d can fix that quickly and boost the immune system. is it okay if i take like 50,000 iu every day for a couple of months to catch up? would that be safe?",
